<li>Thinking of you and your family during this heartbreaking time.  May your memories bring you comfort.</li>
<li>Words cannot express the sorrow I feel for your loss.  Please accept my heartfelt sympathy.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and peace as you grieve the loss of your beloved [deceased's name].</li>
<li>Your family is in my thoughts and prayers. May you find solace in the love you shared.</li>
<li>With deepest sympathy, I offer my condolences to you and your family.</li>
<li>May the beautiful memories of [deceased's name] bring you comfort during this difficult time.</li>
<li>I am so sorry for your loss.  Please know that I'm here for you if you need anything at all.</li>
<li>Holding your family close in my thoughts and prayers.</li>
<li>Sending love and support to your family during this time of sorrow.</li>
<li>My heart goes out to you and your family.  May you find peace in the days ahead.</li>
<li>Please accept my sincere condolences on your heartbreaking loss.</li>
<li>May the love you shared with [deceased's name] bring you peace.</li>
<li>I am so deeply saddened by the news.  Sending you all my love.</li>
<li>Thinking of you and your family. May you find strength in each other's support.</li>
    

